data.quote: Feminism: the radical notion that women are people too!
In a world full of sharks, be a pinky toe - small but mighty enough to make someone curse when they least expect it.
Life is too short for boring shoes and men who don't get feminist jokes.
The pinky toe may be small, but it shoulders an unfair share of furniture encounters.
A pinky toe's strength isn't measured by its size, but by how loudly it makes you yell when it hits the coffee table.
